trans-unit.source: Represents a response of a <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest"></xref>.
When you use the pack URI protocol, you can reference a package and its part elements either locally from inside a package or externally from a Web source.
trans-unit.target: Når du bruker pack URI-protokollen, kan du sjekke en pakke og del elementene enten lokalt fra inni en pakke eller eksternt fra en Web-kilde.

trans-unit.source: For the pack URI protocol, the forward-slash characters (//) of an embedded [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] are represented by commas (,,).
trans-unit.target: For pack URI protokollen skråstrek tegn (/ /) for en innebygd [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] representeres av komma (,).

trans-unit.source: For example: `pack://http:,,www.adatum.com,folder,file.package/images/picture1.jpg` references the file `/images/picture1.jpg` that is contained in `http://www.adatum.com/folder/file.package`.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel: `pack://http:,,www.adatum.com,folder,file.package/images/picture1.jpg` refererer til filen `/images/picture1.jpg` som finnes i `http://www.adatum.com/folder/file.package`.

trans-unit.source: Closes the stream for this request.
Make certain that objects close when they are no longer in use so that resources are not exhausted.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller at objekter lukkes når de er ikke lenger i bruk slik at ressurser ikke er brukt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the content length of the response.
The content length, in bytes.
Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-mime-md.md)] content type of the response stream's content.
If a request does not specify a part in the package, it returns the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] type of the package.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en forespørsel ikke angir en del i pakken, returneres den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] av pakken.

trans-unit.source: Requests that specify a part in the package return one of the following: 1.
trans-unit.target: Forespørsler som angir en del i pakken returnere ett av følgende: 1.

trans-unit.source: If the requested part contains a <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value, the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value is returned.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den forespurte delen inneholder en <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>verdi, i <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>verdien.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the requested part contains no <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value but the stream name contains a recognized [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] extension type, the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] type corresponding to the extension is returned.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den forespurte delen Ingen inneholder <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>verdi, men dataflyten-navnet inneholder et gjenkjent [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] Utvidelsestypen, den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] typen som tilsvarer filtypen returneres.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the requested part does not contain a <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value nor a recognized [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] extension type, ContentType returns an empty string.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den forespurte delen ikke inneholder en <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>verdi eller en gjenkjent [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] Utvidelsestypen, ContentType returnerer en tom streng.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] type of the stream's content.
To be added.
Gets the response stream that is contained in the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter svar dataflyten som ligger i den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The response stream.
Gets the collection of Web <xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*> for this response.
The collection of Web response <xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>.
Gets the inner <xref:System.Net.WebResponse> object for the response.
InnerResponse returns `null` when the response is from the package cache (when <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse.IsFromCache%2A> is `true`).
trans-unit.target: Returnerer InnerResponse `null` når svaret er fra hurtigbufferen pakken (når <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse.IsFromCache%2A>er `true`).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse.IsFromCache%2A>

trans-unit.source: The response data as a <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>.
Gets a value indicating whether the response is from the package cache or from a Web request.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om svaret er fra hurtigbufferen pakken eller en forespørsel.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the response is from the package cache; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the response is from a Web request.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis responsen fra hurtigbufferen pakken; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> hvis responsen fra en forespørsel.

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] of the response.
The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the response.
